8.000Z","msg":"洗乜硬推23條姐<br />\n<br />\nE家有人話要立法會投票都俾一班唔知係弱智定五毛既連登仔屌到屎忽開花<br />\n<br />\n話乜&ldquo;又話廢除功能組別，你投乜撚野&rdquo;&ldquo;你當手足係condom&quot;乜乜柒柒<br />\n一講投票好似殺撚左佢全家咁<br />\n永遠都係諗住一步登天<br />\n仲要加多句&ldquo;準備俾人話係熱狗/五毛&rdquo;，當係免死金牌<br />\n最痴線係話&ldquo;我唔係要建制贏，我要泛民輸&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n有眼都望到建制不停係度拉票<br />\n佢地幾驚唔夠票<br />\n成班白痴就幫埋對家手，叫人咪撚投<br />\n<br />\n到時立法會全部都係奶共派，國歌法送中辱警罪一律都係&ldquo;沒有沒有沒有&rdquo;咁過<br />\n<br />\n仲洗乜23條？"},{"pid":"e6eee046f46cd6ce6d2c377a9225a7edbbbb25f7","tid":1997861,"uid":128981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T05:03:26.000Z","msg":"咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9de2595ba4a821d17623f657ea2244dede0c4c0","tid":1997861,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T05:03:39.000Z","msg":"佢地過到今年八月先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b6a489c0d041e4a011200924e32e9f2352ea7a","tid":1997861,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T05:07:46.000Z","msg":"咁逼切就依加過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8be51c943ac0b8a2cb53af48f1e8935c392cc5","tid":1997861,"uid":126782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T05:16:14.000Z","msg":"建制選到35+再算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年立會泛民一定大勝"},{"pid":"cd04f62a00e7495ada9bb8c14a99464a314b33ee","tid":1997861,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d9fdc18a25b47450efe00284bed0472017706e8","tid":1997861,"uid":210755,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T03:52:42.000Z","msg":"共慘黨比香港人抖啖氣都唔得...係要搞風搞雨....<br />\n香港又有社團條例, 間諜罪, 林林種種罪砌你折磨你,仲有權力唔受制衡嘅執法,法律,司法機構做武器.....仲搞廿三條真係想搞死香港"},"citedBy":1,"repl