:49:41.000Z","msg":"[緊急] 5月2日截止！選民登記自動波填表機(懶人專用)：<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote%2F&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw11UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=0ed9dc52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/bQzfJtv.gif\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然你都可以學大J咁用棍波填表3步曲：<br />\n<br />\n1. 下載表格 ：<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fgcnr.htm&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw11UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=650ebea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/gcnr.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 喺桌面打開表格既PDF檔，輸入個人資料，利用ADOBE PDF既「填寫和簽署」功能，填上電子簽名(注: 直接喺Browser 打開有機會整唔到簽名，所以建議喺資料夾打開檔案）<br />\n<br />\n3. 上載表格：<a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk%2Feto%2Fch%2Findex.jsp&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw11UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=c9359f99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/index.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主求pin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}